                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320105-201-off1116 t18320105-201-crimeloc1118"></join>. On the 19th of December I saw the prisoner take from a chair in the hall a suit of clothes, but he dropped the waistcoat - I ran after him; I saw him throw this coat and trousers over a gentleman's premises - I got a neighbour to assist me, and he took the prisoner, without my losing sight of him; these are the articles - they belong to 
